  ('dietitian-moex-11644', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '那一類烹調方式可能提高食物的致癌作用？ 滷、燉  蒸、汆燙  燴、炒  煙燻、碳烤', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11645', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列激素中，那一項與體內血糖升高無關？ 泌乳激素 (prolactin)  甲狀腺素 (thyroxin)  昇糖素 (glucagon)  腎上腺素 (epinephrine)', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11646', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關Type 2糖尿病的敘述，何者錯誤？ 較不易發生酮酸中毒  大多為成年以後發病  患者大多肥胖  大多以胰島素來控制血糖', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11647', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-092-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者與糖尿病患者發生低血糖無關？ 胰島素劑量過多  習慣的運動量減少  用餐時間延緩  用餐量及次數減少', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2fd7358752e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "092170", "c": "111", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "092", "exam_name": "092年第二次醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、獸醫人員、心理師、呼吸治療師考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
